txt.en: Gertheryg can be found in Arandor.\n\nYou should defeat the gorthorog triplets.
You defeated the three gertheryg that wrought havoc throughout Arandor. The man who posted the bounty will be pleased.

The bounty notice reads:

'Accustomed are we to the foul Orcs and trolls that plague these lands, but the gertheryg are something else, great and terrible! Three such creatures seem to share some form of kinship, and together they maintain control over a large swath of territory.

'Any who can slay these gorthorog monstrosities will be rewarded.'
A bounty notice asks you to find and defeat the gorthorog triplets that control Arandor.
